OL,3,CCouncil to take ice hockey team to
OL,4,Ccourt over #65,000 debt
OL,6,FA local authority is taking an ice
OL,7,Fhockey team to court after it failed
OL,8,Fto keep up with debt repayments.
OL,10,FDumfries and Galloway Council says it
OL,11,Fis owed over #65,000 by DJR Sport Ltd,
OL,12,Fwho run the Solway Sharks.
OL,14,FIn a strongly worded statement, a
OL,15,Fcouncil spokesperson said the team
OL,16,F"has again failed to meet agreed
OL,17,Fcommitments", and that the council had
OL,18,Fpreviously "agreed to revised payments
OL,19,Fand made repeated efforts to resolve
OL,20,Fthe matter".
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1777543609
OL,3,CCouncil to take ice hockey team to
OL,4,Ccourt over #65,000 debt
OL,6,FD&G Council has also vowed to stop
OL,7,Fworking with the Solway Sharks, and
OL,8,Fhas revoked permission to use the
OL,9,FDumfries Ice Bowl.
OL,11,FThe Council said: "Although we are
OL,12,Fproud to support local sport across
OL,13,Fthe region, we have a clear
OL,14,Fresponsibility to safeguard public
OL,15,Ffunds. That duty must take precedence
OL,16,Fhere.
OL,18,F"Other than agreeing uplift of
OL,19,Fequipment, the company will have no
OL,20,Ffurther access to the council's
OL,21,FDumfries Ice Bowl facility."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1777543609
OL,3,CCouncil to take ice hockey team to
OL,4,Ccourt over #65,000 debt
OL,6,FThe Solway Sharks reacted to the news
OL,7,Fon their Facebook page late in the
OL,8,Fevening of Wednesday, April 29.
OL,10,FIn a statement, the ice hockey team
OL,11,Fsaid: "We are extremely disappointed
OL,12,Fto see the Council's statement, which
OL,13,Fpresents only part of the picture.
OL,15,F"The reality is that throughout the
OL,16,F2025`26 season the club operated
OL,17,Fwithout access to key revenue streams,
OL,18,Fincluding the complete loss of bar
OL,19,Fincome, and endured a prolonged period
OL,20,Fwithout practice ice at the start of
OL,21,Fthe season.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,352,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1777543609
OL,3,CCouncil to take ice hockey team to
OL,4,Ccourt over #65,000 debt
OL,6,F"Despite this, the club has continued
OL,7,Fto operate in good faith and has paid
OL,8,Fover #89,000 to the Council under the
OL,9,Fcurrent arrangement.
OL,11,F"We have consistently sought a
OL,12,Fconstructive and realistic discussion
OL,13,Fto resolve the position, taking into
OL,14,Faccount what has actually occurred
OL,15,Fover the last season.
OL,17,F"We remain committed to finding a way
OL,18,Fforward that allows the Solway Sharks
OL,19,Fto continue operating in Dumfries."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
