PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F351A1777543609
OL,3,CCouncil to take ice hockey team to
OL,4,Ccourt over #65,000 debt
OL,6,FSolway Sharks says that if it cannot
OL,7,Ffind a resolution to the situation,
OL,8,F"all sponsorship and season ticket
OL,9,Ffunds will be refunded in full".
OL,11,FThe club added that it has submitted a
OL,12,F"formal complaint against D&G council".
